# my_app Ansible

## Overview
Ansible configuration as code for my_app deployed on DigitalOcean.
Automates server configuration, Docker deployment and Nginx setup for myappguru.net.

## Architecture

Cloudflare (SSL + DDoS)
↓
DigitalOcean Droplet
↓
Nginx (reverse proxy)
↓
Docker container
↓
FastAPI app (my_app)

## Prerequisites
- Ansible 2.9+
- Vault password file at ~/.vault_pass

## Project Structure
my_app_ansible/
├── inventory/
│   └── production/
│       ├── hosts.ini            # production servers (gitignored)
│       └── group_vars/
│           ├── all.yml          # public variables
│           └── vault.yml        # encrypted secrets
├── roles/
│   └── my_app/
│       ├── tasks/
│       │   └── main.yml         # all tasks
│       ├── handlers/
│       │   └── main.yml         # service handlers
│       ├── defaults/
│       │   └── main.yml         # default variables
│       └── templates/
│           └── nginx.conf.j2    # nginx config template
├── playbook.yml                 # main playbook
├── ansible.cfg                  # ansible config (gitignored)
├── .gitignore
└── README.md



## Setup

### 1. Clone the repo

git clone https://github.com/MazPugo/my_app_ansible.git
cd my_app_ansible

### 2. Create vault password file

echo "your-vault-password" > ~/.vault_pass
chmod 600 ~/.vault_pass

### 3. Create inventory file
nano inventory/production/hosts.ini

### 4. Create ansible.cfg

## Usage

### Test connection

ansible web -m ping

### Dry run (check mode)
ansible-playbook playbook.yml --check


### Run full playbook
ansible-playbook playbook.yml
